Results.ReviewText:
Young men do not have a 'teen' section like young ladies do.  Their clothing goes directly from Boys to Men.  It can be difficult to find the right fit.  My son and I are very pleased with the fit, style and comfort of these swim trunks.  We purchased two different prints to last through this summer, I hope!  They do not sag or droop when he gets out of the water, so nothing to see here, girls, he's covered appropriately at all times.  The lighter color fabric of the second pair is appropriate as well.  Since the trunks are lined inside, you cannot see thru when the material is wet. 
-Happy Mother and Child
